    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/14c4ed646ed74f140b315b83e62345fe.avif?t=1770351365\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔王蕾米过着懒散的日子，完全不履行魔王的职责。她的部下们终于忍无可忍，背叛了蕾米，在对她施加了&quot;弱化诅咒&quot;之后，将她扔出了魔王城——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了解除“弱化诅咒”，蕾米需要收集四块由部下们分别持有的“解咒石”。她必须一边解开诅咒，一边全力攻略魔王城。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >究竟蕾米能否解开诅咒，并重新过上懒散的生活呢…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/53ad2370e74daada53bd837b74600c25.avif?t=1770351365\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏是一款动作类RPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将操控蕾米，利用各种技能击败怪物，攻略变成迷宫的魔王城。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/eba9d8cf0c924175a05069d3afdf2020.avif?t=1770351365\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作类RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自由定制操作</p></li></ul>",
